{"tid":251374,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"想搵返一隻舊game","createTime":"2017-05-20T22:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T10:00:28.000Z","uid":11723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2812bfb6182b0ad2a38ae968582af63d654ad78","tid":251374,"uid":11723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T22:42:08.000Z","msg":"隻game應該都起碼十年歷史<br />\n線索有：<br />\n係一隻戰爭game黎<br />\n印象中有劇情玩<br />\n弓手可以用火箭，可以指定一個位置發射唔一定射敵人，例如射草會著火<br />\n就係記得咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fdf308640a0cc57530d10fab7452771a8a16661","tid":251374,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T23:16:26.000Z","msg":"commandor<br />\n好似無咁串"},{"pid":"17b29589d256068aaa6b9d77d3589b9533005322","tid":251374,"uid":11723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T23:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>commandor<br />\n好似無咁串</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成隻game係用冷兵器嘅"},{"pid":"71317dd97dbda76faf644244d061f9ab0a986d0d","tid":251374,"uid":76879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T23:57:03.000Z","msg":"樓主講多d資料<br />\n<br />\n係aoc 果種即時戰略 定係第一人稱？<br />\n<br />\n東方定西方？"},{"pid":"e565f91bf6aec66f6e87c82cb7229455e173334b","tid":251374,"uid":117928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T00:14:24.000Z","msg":"冇資料好難揾架喎"},{"pid":"5c72c92672b42c88a3e179a8a1dd98ffb87106b3","tid":251374,"uid":11723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主講多d資料<br />\n<br />\n係aoc 果種即時戰略 定係第一人稱？<br />\n<br />\n東方定西方？</blockquote><br />\nAoc果種<br />\n東西方就唔多記得<br />\n記得有個兵種係騎馬手握圓盾嘅"},{"pid":"9ac72067cde72fdd603f978d892b79e5444bda1e","tid":251374,"uid":11723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi